span.speech: Þo hede þe wreche fomen I-nowe,

span.text: Þat weren egre him to slete
span.speech: Þat weren egre him to slete

span.text: Mid grete houndes, and to bete.
span.speech: Mid grete houndes, and to bete.

span.text:
Wel and wroþe he wes I-swonge,
Mid staves and speres he wes I-stounge.
Þe wox bicharde him, mid I-wisse,
For he ne fond nones kunnes blisse,
Ne hof duntes forȝevenesse.
